These are Puzzles for 1x4 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-1::.
4 different games are played: chess, scrabble, backgammon, whist
1. the person playing scrabble is in an odd position##4
2. the person playing whist is between the person playing chess and the person playing scrabble##2
3. the person playing whist is on the right of the person playing chess##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2    |    3    |  4   |
| Game   | chess | whist | scrabble | backgammon |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-2::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: writing, board-games, dancing, video-games
1. the person who's hobby is writing is on the left of the person who's hobby is video-games##1
2. the person who's hobby is board-games is in an odd position##4
3. the person who's hobby is board-games is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is writing##3

.:: Answer ::.
|        |   1    |    2    |   3    |   4   |
| Hobby   | board-games | writing | video-games | dancing |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-3::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: yellow, azure, red, ebony
1. the person who likes ebony is on the left or right of the person who likes yellow##3
2. the person who likes yellow is in an odd position##4
3. the person who likes red is between the person who likes ebony and the person who likes azure##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |   2    |    3    |      4       |
| Color   | yellow | ebony | red | azure |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-4::.
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: aconite, daffodil, begonia, lily
1. the person who growsdaffodil is on the left or right of the person who growsaconite##3
2. the person who growsbegonia is in an even position##4
3. the person who growslily is between the person who growsaconite and the person who growsbegonia##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1       |    2     |       3       |   4    |
| Flower   | daffodil | aconite | lily | begonia |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-5::.
City: miami, berlin, boston, marseilles
1. the person traveling to miami is in an even position##4
2. the person traveling to boston is on the right of the person traveling to miami##1
3. the person traveling to berlin is on the left or right of the person traveling to boston##3

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |    2     |    3    |    4     |
| City   | marseilles | miami | boston | berlin |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-6::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: folk, jazz, techno, electronic
1. the fan of jazz is on the far right##1
2. the fan of jazz is on the left or right of the fan of electronic##3
3. the fan of techno is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2     |  3   |    4    |
| Music-Genre   | techno | folk | electronic | jazz |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-7::.
4 different pets are kept: hamster, guinea-pig, ferret, pony
1. the owner of the hamster is on the left or right of the owner of the pony##3
2. the owner of the pony is in an odd position##4
3. the owner of the ferret is between the owner of the hamster and the owner of the guinea-pig##2

.:: Answer ::.
|       |   1    |    2    |      3      |     4      |
| Pet   | pony | hamster | ferret | guinea-pig |

 #################################

 
