.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-19::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: traveling, gardening, card-games, fishing
1. the person who's hobby is gardening is the person who's hobby is gardening##1
2. the person who's hobby is fishing is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is card-games##3
3. the person who's hobby is card-games is on the far left or far right##3
4. the person who's hobby is traveling is in an even position##4
5. the person who's hobby is fishing is on the left of the person who's hobby is gardening##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1     |     2      |   3   |    4    |
| Hobby   | card-games | fishing | gardening | traveling |

